Net-AMQP-Haiku version 0.01
===========================

A Simple Perl Module using Net::AMQP. 

This module is designed to be as simple as possible -- this module
shall only require Net::AMQP to run, and be compatible from Perl
version 5.8.8 and up.

USAGE

use Net::AMQP::Haiku;
my $amqp = Net::AMQP::Haiku->new({
    host=> 'localhost',
    spec_file => '/path/to/spec/file/amqp'
  });
$amqp->open_channel();
$amqp->set_queue('foo');
$amqp->send("ohai!");
print $amqp->receive();

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires only this module:

  Net::AMQP

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

